column4: # 0 -> CC; 1 -> CS; 2 -> CC and CS; 3 -> CC or CS;

# 0 -> Random (no bias); 1 -> Random (center biased); 2 -> Uniform; 3 -> Single colony (layer); 4 -> Single colony (cell); 5 -> Multiple colony (random: mean colony size); 6 -> Multiple colony (random: inoculum size); 7 -> Multiple colony (determined); 8 -> Multiple aggregation (random); 9 -> Load cell placement; 10 -> Uniformity of cell distribution
